1. *Hladno* jutro me je nateralo da obučem jaknu. (*Cold* morning made me put on a jacket.)
2. Čaša vode je *hladna*. (The glass of water is *cold*.)
3. Ne volim kada mi hrana bude *hladna*. (I don't like it when my food is *cold*.)
4. *Hladni* vazduh mi peče lice dok trčim. (*Cold* air is burning my face while I'm running.)
5. Moram da izvadim meso iz zamrzivača i ostavim ga da se odmrzne na *hladnom*. (I need to take out the meat from the freezer and let it thaw in the *cold*.)
6. Leti se najbolje osećam u *hladnoj* vodi. (I feel the best in *cold* water during the summer.)
7. *Hladan* tuš mi je pomogao da se razbudim. (*Cold* shower helped me wake up.)
8. Napolju je *hladno*, obuci kaput. (It's *cold* outside, put on a coat.)
9. Ne verujem da si mogao da pojedeš *hladan* pire krompir. (I can't believe you could eat *cold* mashed potatoes.)
10. *Hladna* zima nas je dočekala ove godine. (*Cold* winter greeted us this year.)